comment.author: 45586426@N06
comment._content:
Despite its content, the Navy Bureau number on tail, 
Modex nose code and squadron indicator are unreadable.
Only the air wing code AF for Reserve Carrier Air Wing Twenty (CVWR-20) is. 

The quality of this picture is not worthy of the 
reputation of the San Diego Air and Space Museum.

Requires deletion and reproduced again with more acceptable quality.
